## 💡 完整解决方案

### 终极方案：解耦控制器

**核心思想**：
同时补偿pitch和yaw的重力耦合，实现真正的解耦控制。

```c
// 在Gimbal_Controller()中实现完整的重力补偿

void Gimbal_Controller()
{
    if (Global.Control.mode != LOCK)
    {
        // === Pitch轴重力补偿 ===
        float pitch_angle = Gimbal.pitch.pitch_location_now;
        float pitch_gravity_comp = Gimbal.pitch.k_gravity * cos(pitch_angle);

        // === Yaw轴重力补偿（新增）===
        // 重心偏移参数（需要实测标定）
        float center_offset_x = 0.0f;  // x方向偏移（米），初始设为0
        float center_offset_y = 0.0f;  // y方向偏移（米），初始设为0

        // 计算yaw轴的重力力矩
        float yaw_angle = Gimbal.small_yaw.small_yaw_location_now;
        float yaw_gravity_torque = 3.04f * 9.8f * (
            center_offset_x * sin(pitch_angle) * cos(yaw_angle) +
            center_offset_y * sin(pitch_angle) * sin(yaw_angle)
        );

        // 转换为电流（GM6020的力矩常数约为0.3 N·m/A）
        float yaw_gravity_current = yaw_gravity_torque / 0.3f;

        // === Pitch控制 ===
        if (Gimbal.pitch.init_flag == 1)
        {
            if (last_mode == LOCK)
            {
                Global.Gimbal.input.pitch = -hipnuc_dev.hi91.pitch;
                Gimbal.pitch.pitch_location_set = degree2rad(Global.Gimbal.input.pitch);
            }

            float pitch_target_motor = Gimbal.pitch.pitch_location_set + Gimbal.pitch.pitch_offset;

            DMMotor_Set(PITCHMotor,
                        pitch_target_motor,
                        0,
                        pitch_gravity_comp,  // pitch重力补偿
                        Gimbal.pitch.kp,
                        Gimbal.pitch.kd);
        }
        else
        {
            DMMotor_Set(PITCHMotor, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.0f);
        }

        // === Yaw控制（加入重力补偿）===
        // 原有的PID控制
        float yaw_control_current = Gimbal.small_yaw.current;

        // 叠加重力补偿
        float yaw_total_current = yaw_control_current + yaw_gravity_current;

        // 限幅
        if (yaw_total_current > GIMBALMOTOR_MAX_CURRENT)
            yaw_total_current = GIMBALMOTOR_MAX_CURRENT;
        if (yaw_total_current < -GIMBALMOTOR_MAX_CURRENT)
            yaw_total_current = -GIMBALMOTOR_MAX_CURRENT;

        DJIMotor_Set(yaw_total_current, SMALLYAWMotor);

        // === 调试输出 ===
        #ifdef DEBUG_COUPLING
        static uint32_t debug_t = 0;
        if (HAL_GetTick() - debug_t > 500) {
            printf("Pitch: %.1f°, Yaw_grav_comp: %.2f A\n",
                   rad2degree(pitch_angle), yaw_gravity_current);
            debug_t = HAL_GetTick();
        }
        #endif
    }
    else
    {
        DMMotor_Set(PITCHMotor, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
        DJIMotor_Set(0, SMALLYAWMotor);
    }

    last_mode = Global.Control.mode;
}
```

